Beaver and Teedyuscung, Chiefs of the Delaware Nation at Allegheny and Wyoming;

Joseph Compass, alias Catepackeaman, Joseph Peepy, Tayshiccomen, Taqualaw, Coun∣sellors to the Chiefs.

